  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_jiaocai_f32828acecb4282c87eaa554d2e1db74e418cd6845843012463a3324028bdd9d.pdf_9_8",
    "text": "Local isn't just a place on a map. It's people: your neighbors and their families, their businesses, farms, nonprofits, events, and recreational venues. Local is a community and all of the opportunities we create together and challenges we work to overcome. Local First has a passion for people living and working together in sustainable community.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.13533835316352158,
