  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_jiaocai_f32828acecb4282c87eaa554d2e1db74e418cd6845843012463a3324028bdd9d.pdf_9_33",
    "text": "Harmony Brewing Company, located in Grand Rapids at 1551 Lake Dr Se, offers rustic wood fired pizzas, with hand prepared dough and a unique twist. Goat cheese is used instead of cheese from cow's milk, providing more flavor with less fat and fewer calories. A great way to enjoy a pizza while still staying within a healthy diet!",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.41917293160025865,
      0.6787790699807993,
      0.607142861674808,
      0.7572674415572653
